1
00:01:06,336 --> 00:01:10,778
=The Truth=

2
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:14,136
=Episode 25=

3
00:01:15,224 --> 00:01:22,040
(Hongfa Mahjong Parlor)

4
00:01:27,310 --> 00:01:28,150
Who's the owner?

5
00:01:31,310 --> 00:01:32,469
Are you here to play mahjong?

6
00:01:32,670 --> 00:01:33,950
All tables are full today.

7
00:01:35,030 --> 00:01:35,909
Maybe another time.

8
00:01:38,808 --> 00:01:39,915
(You're in a camera area.
Mind your actions.)

9
00:01:39,915 --> 00:01:42,262
(Restricted area. Keep out.)

10
00:01:49,030 --> 00:01:49,870
Officer.

11
00:01:51,510 --> 00:01:54,629
This is just a small recreation center.

12
00:01:54,629 --> 00:01:56,749
The residents just come to play

13
00:01:56,749 --> 00:01:57,710
for fun.

14
00:01:57,710 --> 00:01:59,230
Absolutely no illegal activities here.

15
00:01:59,829 --> 00:02:01,590
This place is suspected
of illegal gambling.

16
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:02,430
Take him away.

17
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:04,870
Gambling?

18
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:07,070
This is just a mahjong parlor,
just for fun.

19
00:05:13,590 --> 00:05:15,710
Ye, has your master left?

20
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:18,510
He fell asleep.

21
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,349
He fell asleep?

22
00:05:22,309 --> 00:05:22,989
Ziwu.

23
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,309
Are you heading home?

24
00:05:25,309 --> 00:05:26,229
I can drive you home.

25
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:29,989
I-I'm still waiting for a test result.

26
00:05:29,989 --> 00:05:31,309
So you go ahead.

27
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:32,390
Okay.

28
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,150
Then I...

29
00:06:15,429 --> 00:06:16,229
Thanks.

30
00:06:17,909 --> 00:06:20,150
I came in to bring you something.

31
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:21,309
Then I saw you sleeping.

32
00:06:21,309 --> 00:06:23,150
So I put this on you.

33
00:06:24,349 --> 00:06:26,390
Bring me the milk.

34
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,270
Here.

35
00:06:37,469 --> 00:06:38,270
Sour.

36
00:06:38,989 --> 00:06:39,989
It's yogurt.

37
00:06:52,349 --> 00:06:53,630
Are you biking? Give me a ride.

38
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:55,800
I will have a dinner with my classmate.
Are you going?

39
00:06:56,030 --> 00:06:56,710
No.

40
00:06:56,710 --> 00:06:58,136
I have an early start tomorrow.

41
00:06:59,070 --> 00:06:59,789
Alright.

42
00:07:03,669 --> 00:07:06,150
I saw you checking your phone
constantly.

43
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:07,096
Waiting for messages?

44
00:07:08,349 --> 00:07:08,909
Don't ask.

45
00:07:10,469 --> 00:07:11,429
I told you.

46
00:07:11,429 --> 00:07:13,270
If you like a girl,
go after her and tell her.

47
00:07:13,469 --> 00:07:14,669
Don't bottle it up.

48
00:07:18,789 --> 00:07:21,272
Wait. I'm talking to you.
Why sigh? What's with that look?

49
00:07:21,549 --> 00:07:23,190
What's wrong with you?

50
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,390
Are you giving me a ride?

51
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,549
Brief me on the situation.

52
00:07:27,229 --> 00:07:28,669
We pulled the surveillance footage.

53
00:07:28,669 --> 00:07:30,989
The elevator footage shows

54
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:35,190
that Shanzai
and Haozi appeared at the victim's door

55
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:37,270
an hour before the report was filed.

56
00:07:37,669 --> 00:07:40,869
The time aligns
with the informant's account.

57
00:07:40,869 --> 00:07:42,070
It's basically true.

58
00:07:42,789 --> 00:07:45,590
I reviewed a month's worth of footage.

59
00:07:46,469 --> 00:07:50,710
These two were indeed at the crime scene
for the first time yesterday morning.

60
00:07:51,349 --> 00:07:54,909
The autopsy confirms the time of death
was 8 PM the previous night.

61
00:07:55,030 --> 00:07:58,669
(Zhao Sihui)
If they were there for the first time,

62
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,789
they couldn't commit the crime.

63
00:08:01,669 --> 00:08:04,510
I checked all the footage
from the complex.

64
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,400
That can be confirmed.

65
00:08:07,589 --> 00:08:10,669
We can rule them out as suspects.

66
00:08:11,229 --> 00:08:13,710
What about the 150,000 yuan?

67
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,109
It's verified.

68
00:08:15,309 --> 00:08:17,150
Following Haozi's clues,

69
00:08:17,150 --> 00:08:19,789
we found the mahjong parlor owner
who is engaged in gambling.

70
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:22,789
Zhao Heizi did leave
around 6 PM on the day of the crime,

71
00:08:22,789 --> 00:08:24,669
with 150,000 yuan he won.

72
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:27,190
After he left,
everyone else kept playing.

73
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:27,830
No one left.

74
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:28,950
Footage confirms it.

75
00:08:29,109 --> 00:08:31,390
So 150,000 yuan is our next lead.

76
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:36,270
How did Zhao Heizi carry the money?

77
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,589
It was in a black plastic bag.

78
00:08:37,589 --> 00:08:39,230
He carried the bag by hand when leaving.

79
00:08:40,350 --> 00:08:41,789
Where's the mahjong parlor located?

80
00:08:42,189 --> 00:08:43,829
A private house
near the tunnel entrance.

81
00:08:44,589 --> 00:08:45,990
It's close to the victim's home.

82
00:08:46,069 --> 00:08:48,230
The victim left at 6 PM,

83
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,589
but didn't get home until 8 PM.

84
00:08:49,949 --> 00:08:51,549
Where was he for those two hours?

85
00:08:52,949 --> 00:08:55,709
I also noticed something else
in the footage.

86
00:08:55,709 --> 00:08:56,312
This woman...

87
00:08:56,888 --> 00:08:57,720
(Mistress)

88
00:08:57,829 --> 00:09:00,709
She visited Zhao Heizi's home
multiple times this month.

89
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:05,789
Last month on the 28th,
she even spent the night there.

90
00:09:05,949 --> 00:09:08,350
They had breakfast together
the next morning.

91
00:09:08,990 --> 00:09:12,909
So the victim likely went to see her
after leaving the mahjong parlor.

92
00:09:20,309 --> 00:09:22,270
This neighborhood seems unsafe now.

93
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:23,270
How terrifying.

94
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,949
How could this happen?

95
00:09:25,949 --> 00:09:26,750
How terrifying.

96
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:28,669
Right over there.

97
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:30,870
Be careful, everyone.

98
00:09:30,870 --> 00:09:31,909
Stay back.

99
00:09:32,669 --> 00:09:34,750
Trust the police
and property management.

100
00:09:35,110 --> 00:09:36,750
Something happened
at Zhao Heizi's place.

101
00:09:36,870 --> 00:09:38,270
Isn't his home on the second floor?

102
00:09:38,709 --> 00:09:39,390
Yeah.

103
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:39,949
So horrifying.

104
00:09:39,949 --> 00:09:41,630
This place is not safe anymore.

105
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:42,909
How terrifying.

106
00:09:43,023 --> 00:09:43,909
(Zhao)

107
00:09:43,909 --> 00:09:45,350
How did this happen?

108
00:09:45,350 --> 00:09:46,429
How terrifying!

109
00:09:48,069 --> 00:09:50,549
The footprint trace at the scene

110
00:09:50,589 --> 00:09:51,750
is clear and distinct.

111
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:53,870
It's from a pair of size 41 sneakers.

112
00:09:54,230 --> 00:09:56,088
New soles,
so the shoes were bought recently.

113
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:58,909
At the scene, I only
extracted one type of biological sample.

114
00:09:58,909 --> 00:10:00,470
It was the victim's bloodstain.

115
00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:04,510
However, based on the bloodstain,
we can deduce the entire sequence

116
00:10:04,669 --> 00:10:08,630
of the suspect's actions.
At Zhao Heizi's home,

117
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:12,110
a bloodstain was also extracted
at the main power switch.

118
00:10:12,110 --> 00:10:13,110
There was a lot.

119
00:10:13,949 --> 00:10:16,429
It's inferred that the suspect likely

120
00:10:16,429 --> 00:10:18,589
touched the main power switch
after killing the victim.

121
00:10:19,189 --> 00:10:20,110
This suggests

122
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:25,189
the killer cut the power
before committing the murder.

123
00:10:25,589 --> 00:10:27,270
So, in such complete darkness,

124
00:10:27,589 --> 00:10:30,510
how did the killer
carry out the quick killing?

125
00:10:31,069 --> 00:10:33,230
If we stay long enough in darkness,
we will gradually

126
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:34,750
adapt to see the surroundings.

127
00:10:34,909 --> 00:10:37,030
This is our eyes' ability
to adapt to light.

128
00:11:10,309 --> 00:11:13,990
Right. I looked up some information
to explain this to everyone.

129
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:18,110
The human retina
has cone cells and rod cells.

130
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:20,309
Cone cells only respond
to bright light stimuli.

131
00:11:20,309 --> 00:11:23,510
But at night,
we rely mainly on rod cells to see

132
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:26,630
because rod cells contain substances
sensitive to low light,

133
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:28,150
namely rhodopsin.

134
00:11:28,429 --> 00:11:30,669
Moving suddenly
from bright light into darkness

135
00:11:30,669 --> 00:11:32,350
causes the cone cells
to stop functioning.

136
00:11:32,350 --> 00:11:35,470
The rod cells need time
to resynthesize rhodopsin.

137
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:38,270
This synthesis process
is adaptation to darkness.

138
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:39,709
It usually takes several minutes.

139
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,829
The suspect exploited this fact.

140
00:11:41,829 --> 00:11:43,669
Right after Zhao Heizi
entered the dark room,

141
00:11:43,669 --> 00:11:47,189
he couldn't see temporarily
due to the darkness.

142
00:11:47,189 --> 00:11:49,350
At that moment,
the killer swiftly killed him.

143
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:53,630
The killer came prepared.

144
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:54,470
Yes.

145
00:11:55,470 --> 00:11:56,429
Now look at this.

146
00:11:56,429 --> 00:11:58,829
Based on the traces extracted
from the scene,

147
00:11:58,829 --> 00:12:02,549
all glove prints at the scene
show linear scratch marks.

148
00:12:02,549 --> 00:12:08,150
I infer the gloves worn by the suspect
were made of a very unique material.

149
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:10,669
Based on measurements
of the linear marks,

150
00:12:10,669 --> 00:12:13,549
it's basically confirmed
that they were cut-resistant gloves.

151
00:12:14,669 --> 00:12:16,470
Moreover, after careful observation

152
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:18,350
of the bloodstain distribution
at the scene,

153
00:12:18,789 --> 00:12:20,189
I infer when the victim entered,

154
00:12:20,189 --> 00:12:22,230
he likely wasn't carrying 150,000 yuan.

155
00:12:22,230 --> 00:12:24,510
If the victim had been
carrying the money,

156
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:26,270
during the killing process,

157
00:12:26,309 --> 00:12:28,829
a lot of blood would have gotten
onto the plastic bag.

158
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:30,230
After the murder,

159
00:12:30,230 --> 00:12:32,030
if the suspect took that bag of money,

160
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:34,309
a blank spot would appear
in the blood on the floor.

161
00:12:35,230 --> 00:12:36,309
Surveillance shows

162
00:12:36,309 --> 00:12:38,829
that Zhao Heizi was indeed empty-handed
when returning home.

163
00:12:41,789 --> 00:12:44,150
Ziwu, report your findings.

164
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:48,150
On the red towel found
on the bathroom floor,

165
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,870
I extracted three types of substances.

166
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:51,870
One was the victim's blood.

167
00:12:51,949 --> 00:12:54,630
Another was ordinary sand
and soil particles.

168
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:57,270
The third
had more complex chemical components.

169
00:12:57,429 --> 00:12:59,429
It contains shellac,

170
00:12:59,470 --> 00:13:01,110
pure benzene, ethanol,

171
00:13:01,230 --> 00:13:04,110
rubber, and other chemical compounds.

172
00:13:04,309 --> 00:13:08,589
These chemicals are typically used
for leather finishing oil,

173
00:13:08,589 --> 00:13:11,949
which is generally used
to dye leather jackets

174
00:13:11,990 --> 00:13:13,589
or increase their sheen.

175
00:13:14,309 --> 00:13:17,069
Are you saying that after killing,

176
00:13:17,069 --> 00:13:18,470
the suspect wiped himself

177
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:20,510
with the towel,
leaving the three substances on it?

178
00:13:20,709 --> 00:13:21,270
Yes.

179
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:22,549
A leather jacket?

180
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,549
A black leather jacket.

181
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:27,949
Significant aniline black
was extracted from the towel,

182
00:13:27,949 --> 00:13:29,630
namely, a black dye,

183
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:33,669
meaning it was likely black leather oil.

184
00:13:35,030 --> 00:13:38,350
So, it appears
the killer made thorough preparations.

185
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:42,510
He feared injury
when the victim attacked back.

186
00:13:42,589 --> 00:13:44,189
So he used cut-resistant gloves.

187
00:13:44,549 --> 00:13:46,270
That was his preparation for the murder.

188
00:13:46,669 --> 00:13:48,230
Leather has low permeability.

189
00:13:48,549 --> 00:13:49,870
After blood splattered onto it,

190
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:51,870
it could be easily wiped off
with a towel.

191
00:13:51,990 --> 00:13:53,750
That was his preparation for escaping.

192
00:13:55,069 --> 00:13:57,309
Ye's analysis makes sense.

193
00:13:57,390 --> 00:14:01,270
The killer's primary motive was murder.

194
00:14:02,110 --> 00:14:05,909
This suggests deep animosity
between the killer and the victim.

195
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:08,069
It's highly likely they knew each other.

196
00:14:11,069 --> 00:14:12,549
One more piece of information.

197
00:14:12,789 --> 00:14:14,470
The door shows signs of being pried,

198
00:14:14,470 --> 00:14:16,230
but the lock cylinder shows nothing.

199
00:14:16,709 --> 00:14:18,589
So, it was a non-forced entry,

200
00:14:18,589 --> 00:14:20,630
namely, a non-violent entry.

201
00:14:20,709 --> 00:14:24,549
We now know the suspect entered
beforehand to ambush.

202
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:29,750
So the only plausible entry method
I can think of

203
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:31,750
is using a key.

204
00:14:31,789 --> 00:14:34,150
So, based on this information,

205
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:37,429
we can think about who else might
have keys to the victim's home.

206
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:45,429
Your turn.

207
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:47,870
Did you hear?

208
00:14:47,949 --> 00:14:49,669
A man died in Lvyin Community.

209
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:52,270
They say someone hacked him
to death at home.

210
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:53,949
Is that true?

211
00:14:53,949 --> 00:14:56,870
How could something like this happen?

212
00:14:57,069 --> 00:14:58,309
Of course, it's true.

213
00:14:58,309 --> 00:15:00,270
My sister-in-law lives there.

214
00:15:00,909 --> 00:15:01,949
They said

215
00:15:01,949 --> 00:15:04,350
many police officers showed up
in their community that day.

216
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:06,870
You're giving me goosebumps.

217
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:11,069
I heard that man owed a ton of money.

218
00:15:11,589 --> 00:15:13,750
His wife and kid are in Shanghai.

219
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:16,110
They didn't come back
after getting the news.

220
00:15:16,990 --> 00:15:17,949
Why come back?

221
00:15:18,069 --> 00:15:19,309
He's already dead.

222
00:15:19,470 --> 00:15:21,669
Who knows
if the creditors would target them?

223
00:15:21,669 --> 00:15:22,390
Right?

224
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,069
Yeah.

225
00:15:23,230 --> 00:15:24,669
I've heard about this.

226
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:27,669
I even saw a video about it on my phone.

227
00:15:27,789 --> 00:15:29,309
I wonder if they caught the killer.

228
00:15:31,789 --> 00:15:33,429
Bai Xue, what are you thinking about?

229
00:15:33,429 --> 00:15:34,230
It's your turn.

230
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:36,829
Your talking is giving me a headache.

231
00:15:39,069 --> 00:15:41,350
Where've you been these past few days?

232
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:43,350
I haven't seen you in days.

233
00:15:43,789 --> 00:15:45,589
I've had a terrible headache,

234
00:15:45,589 --> 00:15:46,750
completely unwell.

235
00:15:46,990 --> 00:15:48,110
I stayed at home for days.

236
00:15:50,990 --> 00:15:53,630
A few days ago,
I saw you talking to some guy nearby.

237
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:56,350
You were holding something.
Who was that guy?

238
00:15:56,789 --> 00:15:58,429
He looked pretty sloppy.

239
00:15:58,909 --> 00:15:59,829
A relative of yours?

240
00:16:00,549 --> 00:16:02,350
Now you're gossiping about me?

241
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:04,510
You've got sharp eyes.

242
00:16:05,069 --> 00:16:06,230
I met him outside.

243
00:16:06,350 --> 00:16:07,350
I was just saying hello.

244
00:16:08,069 --> 00:16:09,270
Someone you know outside?

245
00:16:09,630 --> 00:16:11,510
Is he your old flame?

246
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:13,270
Nonsense.

247
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:14,069
By that logic,

248
00:16:14,069 --> 00:16:16,630
every guy who talks to me
on the street is my old flame?

249
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:20,309
Who is it?

250
00:16:27,350 --> 00:16:30,069
Criminal investigation division.
We have some questions for you.

251
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,150
Come with us.

252
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:32,350
- Police.
- Police.

253
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:33,429
- She's in trouble.
- Wait.

254
00:16:33,510 --> 00:16:34,589
They're here to arrest her.

255
00:16:35,069 --> 00:16:36,069
You've seen enough of it.

256
00:16:36,069 --> 00:16:36,909
You may leave.

257
00:16:38,069 --> 00:16:39,510
- Go.
- Hurry up.

258
00:16:47,189 --> 00:16:48,110
Give me another second.

259
00:17:11,320 --> 00:17:12,504
(Conference Room)

260
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:27,990
Bai Xue,

261
00:17:29,190 --> 00:17:32,349
did you know about Zhao Heizi's death?

262
00:17:34,109 --> 00:17:37,030
When I went to his place,
I saw it was sealed off by you.

263
00:17:37,710 --> 00:17:39,309
Everyone's been talking about his death.

264
00:17:39,950 --> 00:17:41,432
I couldn't help but hear about it.

265
00:17:42,629 --> 00:17:44,829
So, what was your relationship
with Zhao Heizi?

266
00:17:47,789 --> 00:17:49,470
Since you brought me here,

267
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:51,109
don't you already know it?

268
00:17:52,069 --> 00:17:52,869
Mistress.

269
00:17:54,789 --> 00:17:56,510
Besides him,

270
00:17:57,149 --> 00:18:00,670
are you also involved with someone else?

271
00:18:04,430 --> 00:18:06,069
I live off men.

272
00:18:06,910 --> 00:18:08,670
I'm not a good woman.

273
00:18:09,829 --> 00:18:11,670
Those men were scared of me

274
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:13,030
asking them to buy me gifts.

275
00:18:13,389 --> 00:18:14,670
They avoided me like the plague.

276
00:18:15,389 --> 00:18:16,990
Who would kill for me?

277
00:18:17,990 --> 00:18:19,030
How ridiculous.

278
00:18:21,309 --> 00:18:24,869
Did you know about Zhao Heizi's family?

279
00:18:26,910 --> 00:18:28,109
I heard from him.

280
00:18:28,990 --> 00:18:30,270
He's not young.

281
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:33,270
His daughter married far away,
and his wife went with her.

282
00:18:33,869 --> 00:18:34,990
He lived alone.

283
00:18:36,230 --> 00:18:37,789
Every day, besides gambling a bit,

284
00:18:38,109 --> 00:18:39,510
he just sought women for amusement.

285
00:18:41,230 --> 00:18:42,670
But he treated me well.

286
00:18:43,149 --> 00:18:44,430
At least, he was generous.

287
00:18:45,389 --> 00:18:47,589
He didn't try
to squeeze anything out of me.

288
00:18:51,470 --> 00:18:56,309
Did Zhao Heizi come
to see you the night he died?

289
00:18:58,549 --> 00:18:59,349
He did.

290
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:08,030
Hello?

291
00:19:09,430 --> 00:19:10,549
I'm downstairs now.

292
00:19:39,109 --> 00:19:39,910
So much money.

293
00:19:40,710 --> 00:19:42,869
If you don't pay them back,
won't they go after you?

294
00:19:45,549 --> 00:19:47,829
I'll drag it out as long as I can.

295
00:19:49,549 --> 00:19:51,629
Once they know
they can't do anything about it,

296
00:19:51,789 --> 00:19:53,750
they might settle for less.

297
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:56,190
Oh, right,

298
00:19:56,389 --> 00:19:57,710
keep this money for me.

299
00:19:58,990 --> 00:20:00,670
We'll spend it later.

300
00:20:02,670 --> 00:20:04,389
Go downstairs and buy some food.

301
00:20:04,549 --> 00:20:05,549
We'll have a drink later.

302
00:20:06,869 --> 00:20:07,670
Okay.

303
00:20:08,190 --> 00:20:10,030
We should have a good drink later.

304
00:20:10,710 --> 00:20:11,869
I'll go buy some food now.

305
00:20:19,349 --> 00:20:22,750
Do you still have that 150,000 yuan?

306
00:20:23,869 --> 00:20:25,549
I brought it here with me.

307
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:29,149
Alright.

308
00:20:30,230 --> 00:20:31,389
Thanks for your cooperation.

309
00:20:40,349 --> 00:20:42,549
Did he suffer when he died?

310
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:46,710
Got it.

311
00:20:47,309 --> 00:20:49,030
Why did you ask?

312
00:20:51,510 --> 00:20:53,670
As I said, he treated me fairly well.

313
00:20:54,230 --> 00:20:55,869
I just hope he could suffer less.

314
00:21:22,789 --> 00:21:23,470
Master.

315
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:26,230
Bai Xue just went to a shop
and bought some funerary objects.

316
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:47,309
Captain Leng.

317
00:21:47,629 --> 00:21:48,109
Come in.

318
00:21:50,030 --> 00:21:51,430
Here's the information on Bai Xue.

319
00:21:51,950 --> 00:21:53,069
Do you still suspect her?

320
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:01,670
You haven't eaten?

321
00:22:03,349 --> 00:22:03,990
Take it.

322
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:05,030
No.

323
00:22:05,030 --> 00:22:06,270
I can't eat them.

324
00:22:07,109 --> 00:22:08,549
Come on. Just eat.

325
00:22:08,549 --> 00:22:09,349
Thanks.

326
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:14,910
Captain Leng, here is...

327
00:22:15,389 --> 00:22:16,069
Ziwu.

328
00:22:16,869 --> 00:22:17,549
Try one.

329
00:22:19,629 --> 00:22:20,470
Just put it here.

330
00:22:27,589 --> 00:22:28,270
Captain Leng.

331
00:22:28,309 --> 00:22:30,589
What's wrong? Is Ziwu getting mad?

332
00:22:36,349 --> 00:22:37,270
Anything else?

333
00:22:38,710 --> 00:22:39,950
I have something else to do.

334
00:22:39,950 --> 00:22:40,869
I have to go.

335
00:23:19,710 --> 00:23:20,829
Found anything?

336
00:23:23,549 --> 00:23:24,629
Nothing significant.

337
00:23:25,270 --> 00:23:26,990
We're lacking leads.

338
00:23:26,990 --> 00:23:28,470
I just came to find more.

339
00:23:29,470 --> 00:23:31,470
But look at the blood spatters.

340
00:23:31,629 --> 00:23:33,510
There really are no blank spots.

341
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:35,710
But if the killer didn't kill for money,

342
00:23:35,710 --> 00:23:37,069
and every stab was fatal,

343
00:23:37,629 --> 00:23:39,389
the only possibility
is a revengeful murder.

344
00:23:39,829 --> 00:23:42,230
Bai Xue is already cleared, right?

345
00:23:44,309 --> 00:23:45,430
I checked the door lock.

346
00:23:46,309 --> 00:23:48,430
There are only marks made by Haozi.

347
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:54,349
Unlike the one in the room,
this character "Fu" is put upside down.

348
00:23:57,629 --> 00:23:58,629
Someone moved it.

349
00:24:01,549 --> 00:24:02,629
You're right.

350
00:24:04,190 --> 00:24:05,430
Given the dust on this tape,

351
00:24:05,430 --> 00:24:07,190
it must have been moved recently.

352
00:24:13,069 --> 00:24:14,149
That makes sense now.

353
00:24:14,910 --> 00:24:17,270
The suspect probably picked the lock
from here.

354
00:25:14,230 --> 00:25:14,829
Liu Yang.

355
00:25:15,230 --> 00:25:17,230
Check with Zhao Heizi's daughter

356
00:25:17,470 --> 00:25:20,910
and ask her if they came back
for Zhao Heizi's birthday in 2023

357
00:25:21,389 --> 00:25:22,389
and took a family photo.

358
00:25:22,910 --> 00:25:24,349
Also, who was there on his birthday?

359
00:25:24,549 --> 00:25:25,230
Right now.

360
00:25:32,789 --> 00:25:34,430
The length of this kind of tool

361
00:25:34,430 --> 00:25:37,789
is determined
based on the lock's position.

362
00:25:38,030 --> 00:25:39,910
Usually, for portability,

363
00:25:40,589 --> 00:25:41,910
it's mostly assembled on-site.

364
00:25:41,910 --> 00:25:46,109
Just with some metal rods and bolts.

365
00:25:46,109 --> 00:25:46,750
It's simple.

366
00:25:51,389 --> 00:25:52,190
Master.

367
00:25:52,389 --> 00:25:53,910
Lei wants us to look at the footage.

368
00:25:54,549 --> 00:25:56,789
Based on Long's analysis

369
00:25:56,789 --> 00:26:00,030
and the clothing details Ziwu provided,

370
00:26:00,030 --> 00:26:01,950
I found this suspect.

371
00:26:03,470 --> 00:26:06,829
This is footage
from the east gate camera.

372
00:26:07,230 --> 00:26:09,030
When the suspect entered,

373
00:26:09,030 --> 00:26:11,109
his hands were empty, carrying nothing.

374
00:26:11,430 --> 00:26:13,030
Now look here.

375
00:26:14,270 --> 00:26:16,589
This is him leaving the complex.

376
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:20,149
Again, his hands were empty,
carrying nothing.

377
00:26:20,510 --> 00:26:22,109
According to Long's analysis,

378
00:26:22,629 --> 00:26:27,750
he likely used something
like a peephole or a lock-picking tool.

379
00:26:28,109 --> 00:26:29,869
Long, how do you explain this?

380
00:26:32,069 --> 00:26:34,069
Either he had an accomplice,

381
00:26:34,069 --> 00:26:35,430
or otherwise...

382
00:26:39,629 --> 00:26:40,230
Master.

383
00:26:40,950 --> 00:26:43,309
Lei, what about the elevator footage?

384
00:26:43,869 --> 00:26:44,510
None.

385
00:26:44,910 --> 00:26:46,829
He probably didn't use the elevator.

386
00:26:46,829 --> 00:26:47,750
He took the stairs.

387
00:26:48,549 --> 00:26:51,109
Right, I confirmed that.

388
00:26:51,349 --> 00:26:54,149
I found his footprints in the stairwell.

389
00:26:54,829 --> 00:26:55,510
Jiao.

390
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:56,629
I have an idea.

391
00:26:56,829 --> 00:26:59,470
Cut out the images
of the suspect from both video clips.

392
00:27:00,789 --> 00:27:02,670
Resize them proportionally
to the same scale.

393
00:27:07,750 --> 00:27:08,510
Okay.

394
00:27:10,149 --> 00:27:13,430
Take a look. Found anything?

395
00:27:21,589 --> 00:27:24,549
When the suspect entered the complex,
his abdomen was slightly protruding.

396
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:27,670
But after he left, it looked flat.

397
00:27:28,510 --> 00:27:33,230
So he must have hidden the tools
inside his clothes.

398
00:27:33,230 --> 00:27:36,389
After killing, he discarded the tools
somewhere inside the complex.

399
00:27:38,789 --> 00:27:41,109
Contact the property management
immediately.

400
00:27:41,549 --> 00:27:43,750
Re-check all cleaning staff

401
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:44,670
dumping the trash

402
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:45,789
for that day.

403
00:27:46,670 --> 00:27:48,349
And find the tools.

404
00:27:48,990 --> 00:27:49,470
Go now.

405
00:27:49,470 --> 00:27:49,950
Yes.

406
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:51,710
Master.

407
00:27:52,430 --> 00:27:53,589
I think

408
00:27:54,069 --> 00:27:55,349
she must know something.

409
00:28:36,629 --> 00:28:37,430
Found something.

410
00:28:41,349 --> 00:28:43,349
I have a plan
to play mahjong with friends today.

411
00:28:44,389 --> 00:28:47,430
What brings you here again?

412
00:28:50,149 --> 00:28:53,629
On Zhao Heizi's birthday last July,

413
00:28:54,670 --> 00:28:55,510
were you there?

414
00:28:56,470 --> 00:28:57,270
Sure.

415
00:28:58,030 --> 00:29:00,069
Last year,
he had a falling out with his family.

416
00:29:00,389 --> 00:29:01,829
His wife and kid didn't come back.

417
00:29:02,270 --> 00:29:03,589
I spent his birthday with him.

418
00:29:04,069 --> 00:29:05,230
Did you take photos?

419
00:29:06,589 --> 00:29:07,389
Yes.

420
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:11,470
Isn't that photo displayed
in his cabinet?

421
00:29:12,069 --> 00:29:13,470
That photo is missing.

422
00:29:15,589 --> 00:29:16,789
I didn't know it.

423
00:29:17,190 --> 00:29:18,750
Maybe he put it away.

424
00:29:19,430 --> 00:29:20,389
Why did you ask?

425
00:29:23,109 --> 00:29:27,710
It's highly likely
that the murderer took that photo.

426
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:31,510
Anything you want to say?

427
00:29:32,190 --> 00:29:33,190
Or anyone you suspect?

428
00:29:34,950 --> 00:29:36,030
Officer Ye?

429
00:29:36,710 --> 00:29:38,030
I can call you that, right?

430
00:29:39,349 --> 00:29:43,510
Are you suggesting
the murderer did it for me?

431
00:29:45,869 --> 00:29:47,430
I've already told you.

432
00:29:49,589 --> 00:29:50,950
I'm not a good woman.

433
00:29:51,549 --> 00:29:53,549
Men avoided me like the plague.

434
00:29:54,230 --> 00:29:56,190
Who would kill for me?

435
00:29:58,910 --> 00:29:59,990
You're a man too.

436
00:30:00,549 --> 00:30:01,710
For a woman,

437
00:30:02,510 --> 00:30:03,629
would you do that?

438
00:30:08,309 --> 00:30:10,520
The fact that I wouldn't
doesn't mean others wouldn't.

439
00:30:10,829 --> 00:30:12,109
Whether you tell truth or lies,

440
00:30:13,430 --> 00:30:16,349
it'll all be clear
once we catch the killer.

441
00:30:27,629 --> 00:30:29,349
I've already verified with Bai Xue.

442
00:30:29,510 --> 00:30:30,950
On Zhao Heizi's birthday last year,

443
00:30:31,190 --> 00:30:36,549
they took a photo
and displayed it with a family portrait.

444
00:30:36,589 --> 00:30:38,950
But after the crime,
that photo disappeared.

445
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:48,470
You think Bai Xue is hiding something?

446
00:30:48,990 --> 00:30:51,789
Bai Xue keeps insisting
it's unrelated to her past.

447
00:30:51,910 --> 00:30:54,549
But since the killer took that photo,

448
00:30:55,030 --> 00:30:58,349
I believe
the killer not only knows Bai Xue,

449
00:30:58,869 --> 00:30:59,990
but has a history with her.

450
00:31:04,589 --> 00:31:05,389
Liu Yang.

451
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:07,430
Look into Bai Xue again,

452
00:31:07,950 --> 00:31:11,710
and try to find any suspicious points
we overlooked before.

453
00:31:11,710 --> 00:31:12,389
Okay.

454
00:31:46,750 --> 00:31:47,349
Hello?

455
00:31:47,470 --> 00:31:48,190
Captain Leng.

456
00:31:48,190 --> 00:31:48,910
- Ziwu.
- Found it.

457
00:31:48,910 --> 00:31:51,670
On lock-picking tool's threaded
connector, I detected a DNA sample.

458
00:31:51,910 --> 00:31:53,470
It's from a male, with a prior record.

459
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:55,309
I'll bring the information to you now.

460
00:31:55,309 --> 00:31:55,910
Good.

461
00:32:18,670 --> 00:32:19,309
Hello?

462
00:32:19,549 --> 00:32:20,190
Hello?

463
00:32:20,430 --> 00:32:21,589
Is this Lu Jun?

464
00:32:22,710 --> 00:32:24,030
Is everything ready?

465
00:32:24,349 --> 00:32:25,149
It's ready.

466
00:32:27,549 --> 00:32:29,750
Good. I'll be there soon.

467
00:32:30,230 --> 00:32:30,670
Okay.

468
00:32:35,549 --> 00:32:36,789
I looked into him.

469
00:32:36,789 --> 00:32:37,990
Lu Jun, male.

470
00:32:37,990 --> 00:32:40,309
He was born on August 12, 1984.

471
00:32:40,309 --> 00:32:41,309
In 2002,

472
00:32:41,309 --> 00:32:43,430
he was sentenced for intentional assault

473
00:32:43,510 --> 00:32:45,848
and released in 2019.
In January two years ago,

474
00:32:45,848 --> 00:32:48,020
(Information on Lu Jun)
he was sent to a drug rehab.

475
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:50,200
He just got released this January.

476
00:32:50,710 --> 00:32:52,750
Only two months after that, he murdered.

477
00:32:53,710 --> 00:32:55,990
When you
investigated the victim's connections,

478
00:32:56,389 --> 00:32:57,389
was this man involved?

479
00:32:57,910 --> 00:32:58,950
No, he wasn't.

480
00:33:01,670 --> 00:33:02,470
Ye Qian,

481
00:33:03,430 --> 00:33:04,990
find this man first.

482
00:33:05,950 --> 00:33:06,750
Understood.

483
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:36,670
Hello.

484
00:33:36,829 --> 00:33:37,629
Police.

485
00:33:37,990 --> 00:33:39,030
Which room is Lu Jun in?

486
00:33:39,230 --> 00:33:39,869
One moment.

487
00:33:40,470 --> 00:33:41,149
Room 303.

488
00:33:41,750 --> 00:33:42,589
Is he there now?

489
00:33:42,789 --> 00:33:44,069
I'm not sure about that.

490
00:33:44,349 --> 00:33:45,149
Give me the key.

491
00:33:45,149 --> 00:33:45,869
Okay.

492
00:34:24,069 --> 00:34:24,870
Police!

493
00:34:26,790 --> 00:34:27,589
Police!

494
00:34:29,709 --> 00:34:30,749
No one. Turn on the light.

495
00:34:53,176 --> 00:34:59,640
(Li Guohua, Funeral Services)

496
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:13,669
Captain Leng.

497
00:35:14,149 --> 00:35:16,629
I just contacted Li Guohua
from Zhongxiao Funeral Services.

498
00:35:16,629 --> 00:35:19,549
A year ago, Lu Jun asked his brother
to buy a burial plot.

499
00:35:19,830 --> 00:35:20,549
A few days ago,

500
00:35:20,549 --> 00:35:22,950
he called to inquire
about the burial plot maintenance fee.

501
00:35:22,950 --> 00:35:24,589
He will go to pay the fee today.

502
00:35:24,910 --> 00:35:26,149
I've gotten the address.

503
00:35:27,870 --> 00:35:28,510
Let's go.

504
00:35:28,830 --> 00:35:29,549
Go.

505
00:35:30,910 --> 00:35:31,709
Check your gear.

506
00:35:56,248 --> 00:35:59,704
(Beloved Wife)

507
00:36:05,870 --> 00:36:06,669
Mengqing.

508
00:36:08,510 --> 00:36:11,310
Very soon, I'll see you

509
00:36:12,950 --> 00:36:14,229
and our child again.

510
00:36:15,069 --> 00:36:17,589
The three of us
will finally be together.

511
00:36:23,549 --> 00:36:26,510
No one will ever hurt you again.

512
00:36:59,390 --> 00:37:00,109
Lu Jun.

513
00:37:01,189 --> 00:37:02,870
Since we've found you,

514
00:37:03,189 --> 00:37:05,629
we hope you'll cooperate fully
with our investigation.

515
00:37:10,549 --> 00:37:13,310
You probably already know my background.

516
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:15,870
I killed someone before.

517
00:37:16,870 --> 00:37:18,749
If I hadn't turned myself in,

518
00:37:19,470 --> 00:37:21,069
I wouldn't be sitting here today.

519
00:37:22,189 --> 00:37:24,629
I'm not saying this
for any other reason.

520
00:37:25,310 --> 00:37:26,269
I will cooperate.

521
00:37:27,269 --> 00:37:28,629
Did you kill Zhao Heizi?

522
00:37:28,669 --> 00:37:29,229
Yes.

523
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:32,549
Killing him fulfilled my final wish.

524
00:37:33,149 --> 00:37:34,069
What wish?

525
00:37:34,790 --> 00:37:36,189
He caused my wife's death.

526
00:37:37,549 --> 00:37:38,549
Who was your wife?

527
00:37:39,549 --> 00:37:40,430
Wang Mengqing.

528
00:37:41,470 --> 00:37:44,149
Actually,
I've held a lot inside for years.

529
00:37:45,149 --> 00:37:48,189
After getting it out, I can face my end.

530
00:37:50,149 --> 00:37:53,269
Back in 2000, I was 16.

531
00:37:54,390 --> 00:37:55,830
My family was poor

532
00:37:56,069 --> 00:37:57,350
and couldn't raise all the kids.

533
00:37:58,269 --> 00:38:00,269
So I had to start
to work in my early days.

534
00:38:01,390 --> 00:38:04,470
I had almost no money when I left home.

535
00:38:05,709 --> 00:38:08,629
So I just wanted
to find a job to support myself.

536
00:38:10,229 --> 00:38:12,430
I took a job as a bartender in a bar.

537
00:38:13,269 --> 00:38:14,549
Pay was lousy.

538
00:38:15,390 --> 00:38:16,470
But that's where

539
00:38:17,950 --> 00:38:19,189
I met Mengqing.

540
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:23,350
I remember one night,

541
00:38:24,749 --> 00:38:26,749
Mengqing was drinking
with two customers.

542
00:38:27,269 --> 00:38:29,390
She got drunk and went to the restroom.

543
00:38:30,790 --> 00:38:32,510
(Liu Yang, look into Wang Mengqing.)
I overheard

544
00:38:33,430 --> 00:38:34,589
that those two guys planned

545
00:38:34,589 --> 00:38:36,990
to take her to a motel
when she came out.

546
00:38:37,950 --> 00:38:41,910
One of them slipped something
into her drink while saying it.

547
00:38:42,790 --> 00:38:43,870
I couldn't stand it.

548
00:38:44,709 --> 00:38:46,229
When Mengqing came out,

549
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:48,229
I got her away.

550
00:38:50,149 --> 00:38:51,310
That night, to thank me,

551
00:38:52,310 --> 00:38:53,830
she treated me to barbecue.

552
00:38:54,189 --> 00:38:55,709
She told me a lot then.

553
00:38:56,430 --> 00:38:57,910
I could tell

554
00:38:58,269 --> 00:39:00,790
she was carrying heavy burdens too.

555
00:39:03,229 --> 00:39:04,910
Her family was poor too.

556
00:39:05,910 --> 00:39:07,470
To take care of her grandparents,

557
00:39:07,950 --> 00:39:09,830
she started working at 14.

558
00:39:11,870 --> 00:39:14,189
We totally understood each other.

559
00:39:15,830 --> 00:39:19,229
We drank all night that day.

560
00:39:21,749 --> 00:39:22,669
After that night,

561
00:39:23,669 --> 00:39:25,109
we got together.

562
00:39:26,390 --> 00:39:28,310
To spare my feelings,

563
00:39:28,669 --> 00:39:30,629
she quit her job in the bar

564
00:39:31,229 --> 00:39:33,109
and got a job
as a waitress at a restaurant.

565
00:39:34,069 --> 00:39:36,109
Things were fine at first.

566
00:39:37,669 --> 00:39:39,910
But after three months,

567
00:39:42,390 --> 00:39:43,910
I discovered her secret.

568
00:39:45,229 --> 00:39:46,109
What secret?

569
00:39:47,910 --> 00:39:48,990
Mengqing was using drugs.

570
00:39:50,310 --> 00:39:51,149
What drug?

571
00:39:51,149 --> 00:39:51,950
Heroin.

572
00:39:52,910 --> 00:39:54,990
A customer dragged her into it.

573
00:39:56,189 --> 00:39:58,229
She thought I'd leave her once I knew.

574
00:39:59,030 --> 00:40:00,390
But I told her

575
00:40:00,749 --> 00:40:01,669
that no matter what,

576
00:40:02,310 --> 00:40:03,709
I would always love her.

577
00:40:04,269 --> 00:40:05,030
Mengqing,

578
00:40:05,950 --> 00:40:07,470
no matter what you become,

579
00:40:07,990 --> 00:40:09,470
you're the one I love.

580
00:40:13,950 --> 00:40:15,390
Maybe because of those words,

581
00:40:16,669 --> 00:40:18,950
she was determined to quit.

582
00:40:23,149 --> 00:40:26,189
Those were our toughest six months.

583
00:40:28,229 --> 00:40:29,790
I worked two jobs every day,

584
00:40:30,390 --> 00:40:34,149
just hoping to open our own shop sooner.

585
00:40:36,910 --> 00:40:38,510
Later, we saved up some money.

586
00:40:38,950 --> 00:40:40,310
We also borrowed some.

587
00:40:42,350 --> 00:40:47,790
I remember
it was Children's Day, June 1st, 2001.

588
00:40:49,109 --> 00:40:50,470
We rented a storefront

589
00:40:51,350 --> 00:40:52,549
and opened a small restaurant.

590
00:40:53,990 --> 00:40:56,510
We thought
we could finally live normal lives.

591
00:40:58,709 --> 00:41:02,990
But a few days after the opening,

592
00:41:03,790 --> 00:41:05,350
trouble came.

593
00:41:06,709 --> 00:41:09,870
They told me
if we wanted to run a shop there,

594
00:41:10,790 --> 00:41:12,870
we had to
buy fixed amounts of ingredients

595
00:41:13,589 --> 00:41:15,549
from them every day.

596
00:41:16,709 --> 00:41:18,109
Fixed amounts?

597
00:41:18,589 --> 00:41:19,229
Yes.

598
00:41:19,990 --> 00:41:22,189
They didn't care
if my business was good or bad.

599
00:41:22,790 --> 00:41:26,069
I had to spend 200 yuan
on buying things from them every day.

600
00:41:26,510 --> 00:41:28,549
And the stuff they gave us
are pure garbage.

601
00:41:29,069 --> 00:41:30,149
Rotten vegetables

602
00:41:30,149 --> 00:41:31,030
and spoiled pork.

603
00:41:31,669 --> 00:41:33,749
I found them completely inedible.

604
00:41:34,189 --> 00:41:35,589
So I rejected them.

605
00:41:37,950 --> 00:41:38,870
Did you file a report?

606
00:41:40,229 --> 00:41:41,030
I wish I could.

607
00:41:42,390 --> 00:41:43,790
Before I could even file a report,

608
00:41:44,709 --> 00:41:47,749
their leader,
a guy called Monkey, came to warn me.

609
00:41:48,749 --> 00:41:50,870
He said this area was his territory.

610
00:41:51,669 --> 00:41:55,030
If I wanted to do business here,
I had to follow his rules.

611
00:41:55,510 --> 00:41:56,589
Otherwise, I had to leave.

612
00:41:57,629 --> 00:41:59,870
I was only 18 then,
young and hot-headed.

613
00:42:01,069 --> 00:42:03,149
So I ended up fighting him
right there in the shop.

614
00:42:04,189 --> 00:42:06,350
I slashed Monkey's head with a knife.

615
00:42:07,350 --> 00:42:11,629
Because of that,
I was detained for 15 days.

616
00:42:12,669 --> 00:42:14,470
During my detention,

617
00:42:14,830 --> 00:42:16,229
they went to Mengqing.

618
00:42:16,749 --> 00:42:19,430
They told her
to prepare a coffin for me.

619
00:42:19,870 --> 00:42:22,069
They said they'd kill me
the moment I was released.

620
00:42:25,089 --> 00:42:28,582
♪Replacing the weight of tears
with that of sweat♪

621
00:42:32,376 --> 00:42:37,697
♪Covering the gunshot's sound
with wounds♪

622
00:42:39,770 --> 00:42:44,624
♪No one is born unyielding and strong♪

623
00:42:45,430 --> 00:42:48,577
♪But because someone
always rushes ahead♪

624
00:42:48,577 --> 00:42:51,681
♪To shield us from the storm♪

625
00:42:54,337 --> 00:42:59,471
♪When every extraordinary act
becomes routine♪

626
00:43:01,441 --> 00:43:07,073
♪Just to polish the badge
upon their shoulder♪

627
00:43:08,833 --> 00:43:12,417
♪Like light surging unseen
through the night♪

628
00:43:13,569 --> 00:43:21,009
♪Converging into your form♪

629
00:43:21,441 --> 00:43:24,119
♪Looking up♪

630
00:43:24,119 --> 00:43:27,658
♪Such dazzling glory♪

631
00:43:28,641 --> 00:43:31,201
♪Like hope♪

632
00:43:31,201 --> 00:43:35,134
♪Reaching out its arms♪

633
00:43:36,001 --> 00:43:38,653
♪Cloaked in light♪

634
00:43:38,653 --> 00:43:43,137
♪Alone, they charge ahead♪

635
00:43:43,137 --> 00:43:45,953
♪Traversing♪

636
00:43:45,953 --> 00:43:52,464
♪The battlefield of fate♪
